Ludwig - a lattice Boltzmann code for complex fluids

The ./docs directory contains the manual in tex form, and as
a pdf. This includes a quickstart guide for compilation and
running the code.

The ./src directory contains the main src code.

License details are given in the ./LICENSE file

* Contact

Ludwig is available from

http://ccpforge.cse.rl.ac.uk/gf/project/ludwig/

Please contact support@epcc.ed.ac.uk if you have any questions
and quote "Ludwig" in the subject line.
 